::DarkMouse::

She looked up at paralysis and then to Quickstrike.  She was a little 
worried.  She only had her optic lazars.  All her other weapons were 
gone.  She remembered her lock pick set and burglery kit.  But that 
wouldn't be much help in a battle like this one was turning into. She 
looked up at Quickstrike and whispered,"Good to be fighting with you 
again commander."
